data.text:
Going to be re-releasing my audio/video podcast called the Hot Sauce. Will be interviewing a number of professionals in the food and nutrition world and let them tell their stories and inspire the next generation of Registered Dietitian Nutritionists https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLKN8ovn9IbnAAf5RMjX76o7ZUKXB4OYPs

I worked on a video featuring foods of China, India, The Phillipines, Vietnam, Korea, Japan, and Thailand. You can watch the videos here https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLKN8ovn9IbnBjX3fYYe0XzObD39TNe2nO
